                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410104-440-offence-1 t18410104-cd-31"></join>19th of December</rs>, 4 1/2 lbs. weight of pork, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18410104-name-211" type="victimName">
